        <p>Israel is a country in Western Asia, with borders touching Lebanon, Syria, Jordan, the Palestinian territories and Egypt. It is located on the southeastern shore of the Mediterranean Sea and the northern shore of the Red Sea. The rich history, diversity and cultural landmarks makes Israel an incredible destination for traveling.</p>
